pull.title: [depends] builders: No need to set -L and --location for curl
pull.body: `-L` and  `--location` do the same; No need to set both.

ACK https://github.com/MarcoFalke/bitcoin/commit/fa7a5c54fc836ada12c185c43806c5e4a1044701

```
 -L, --location      Follow redirects (H)
     --location-trusted  Like '--location', and send auth to other hosts (H)
     --login-options OPTIONS  Server login options (IMAP, POP3, SMTP)
```
